Today's recipe for Suji ka Halwa is very easy to make and a huge favorite among all.

00:00:17.651 --> 00:00:20.159
Ingredients required:

00:00:20.679 --> 00:00:21.329
Suji (semolina) - 1/2 cup

00:00:22.204 --> 00:00:28.143
Sugar - a bit more than 1/2 cup or as you desire

00:00:28.721 --> 00:00:30.570
Ghee - 1/3 cup

00:00:31.119 --> 00:00:32.928
Almonds - 8 to 10

00:00:33.376 --> 00:00:34.916
Cashew nuts - 10 to 12

00:00:35.457 --> 00:00:37.759
Raisins - 1 tbsp

00:00:38.293 --> 00:00:42.352
Elaichi (cardamom) - 4 (peel and crush)

