00:01:05.107 --> 00:01:06.884
Now put Suji in the Ghee

00:01:07.060 --> 00:01:13.595
and roast Suji till it turns brown while stirring continuously.

00:01:16.658 --> 00:01:22.083
Suji should not stick to the bottom of the pan.

00:01:26.154 --> 00:01:40.150
Roast the Suji some more on a low flame till it turns dark brown.

00:01:52.585 --> 00:02:00.613
On a low flame add water to the roasted Suji.

00:02:00.848 --> 00:02:11.753
As we have taken 1/2 cup Suji we will put 4 times more water in it.

00:02:34.081 --> 00:02:36.010
Now add sugar

00:02:37.538 --> 00:02:50.238
and cook Suji on a medium flame till the sugar dissolves and Suji puffs in the water.

