00:04:03.986 --> 00:04:05.113
Turn off the gas.

00:04:09.985 --> 00:04:12.779
Garnish Halwa with the remaining cashew nuts.

00:04:23.666 --> 00:04:29.121
Suji ka Halwa is ready, it does not consume much cooking time.

